
"smart_sources:Research/@tan_interdisciplinary_2021.md": {"path":"Research/@tan_interdisciplinary_2021.md","last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"last_read":{"hash":"1nq4p2p","at":1774951884833},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1774951829804,"size":3475,"at":1774951884833,"hash":"1nq4p2p"},"blocks":{"#---frontmatter---":[1,96],"#Interdisciplinary Research in Alzheimer's Disease and the Roles International Societies Can Play.":[98,102],"#Interdisciplinary Research in Alzheimer's Disease and the Roles International Societies Can Play.#{1}":[100,102]},"outlinks":[{"title":"Author/Shawn Zheng Kai Tan","target":"Author/Shawn Zheng Kai Tan","line":75},{"title":"Author/Zks Tan","target":"Author/Zks Tan","line":76},{"title":"Author/Shawn Tan","target":"Author/Shawn Tan","line":77},{"title":"Author/Robert Chunhua Zhao","target":"Author/Robert Chunhua Zhao","line":78},{"title":"Author/R. C. Zhao","target":"Author/R. C. Zhao","line":79},{"title":"Author/Robert Chunhua Zhao","target":"Author/Robert Chunhua Zhao","line":80},{"title":"Author/Sasanka Chakrabarti","target":"Author/Sasanka Chakrabarti","line":81},{"title":"Author/S. Chakrabarti","target":"Author/S. Chakrabarti","line":82},{"title":"Author/Sasanka Chakrabarti","target":"Author/Sasanka Chakrabarti","line":83},{"title":"Author/Ilia Stambler","target":"Author/Ilia Stambler","line":84},{"title":"Author/Ilia Stambler","target":"Author/Ilia Stambler","line":85},{"title":"Author/Ilia Stambler","target":"Author/Ilia Stambler","line":86},{"title":"Author/I. Stambler","target":"Author/I. Stambler","line":87},{"title":"Author/Kunlin Jin","target":"Author/Kunlin Jin","line":88},{"title":"Author/Kunlin Jin","target":"Author/Kunlin Jin","line":89},{"title":"Author/K. Jin","target":"Author/K. Jin","line":90},{"title":"Author/Lee Wei Lim","target":"Author/Lee Wei Lim","line":91},{"title":"Author/Lee Wei Lim","target":"Author/Lee Wei Lim","line":92}],"metadata":{"id":"tan_interdisciplinary_2021","type":"article-journal","title":"Interdisciplinary Research in Alzheimer's Disease and the Roles International Societies Can Play.","issued":{"date-parts":[[2021]]},"DOI":"null","container-title":"null","abstract":"An ever-increasing ageing population has elevated Alzheimer's disease to be one of the biggest challenges in modern medicine. Alzheimer's disease is highly complex, and we are still no closer to understanding the causes, let alone an effective treatment. The lack of good experimental models and lack of critical understanding has led to high failure rates of clinical trials with high associated costs, as well as difficulties in implementing treatments. The multifaceted nature of this disease highlights the need for an interdisciplinary approach to address these concerns. In this essay, we suggest how collaborative work can be useful in addressing some of the above issues. We then propose that international organisations and publishers need to support interdisciplinary research by creating platforms, lobbying funders, and pushing for interdisciplinary publications. We further highlight some of the issues involved in implementing these suggestions and argue that willpower of the research community, together with a re-evaluation of evaluation metrics and incentive systems, are needed in order to foster interdisciplinary research. Overall, we emphasise the need for interdisciplinary research in Alzheimer's disease and suggest that international societies should play a huge role in this endeavour.","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"Tan","given":"Shawn Zheng Kai","literal":""},{"family":"Tan","given":"Zks","literal":""},{"family":"Tan","given":"Shawn","literal":""},{"family":"Zhao","given":"Robert Chunhua","literal":""},{"family":"Zhao","given":"R. C.","literal":""},{"family":"Zhao","given":"Robert Chunhua","literal":""},{"family":"Chakrabarti","given":"Sasanka","literal":""},{"family":"Chakrabarti","given":"S.","literal":""},{"family":"Chakrabarti","given":"Sasanka","literal":""},{"family":"Stambler","given":"Ilia","literal":""},{"family":"Stambler","given":"Ilia","literal":""},{"family":"Stambler","given":"Ilia","literal":""},{"family":"Stambler","given":"I.","literal":""},{"family":"Jin","given":"Kunlin","literal":""},{"family":"Jin","given":"Kunlin","literal":""},{"family":"Jin","given":"K.","literal":""},{"family":"Lim","given":"Lee Wei","literal":""},{"family":"Lim","given":"Lee Wei","literal":""}],"citation-key":"tan_interdisciplinary_2021","year":"2021","dateCreated":"2026-03-31","reading-status":"to-read","aliases":["Interdisciplinary Research in Alzheimer's Disease and the Roles International Societies Can Play."],"author-links":["[[Author/Shawn Zheng Kai Tan]]","[[Author/Zks Tan]]","[[Author/Shawn Tan]]","[[Author/Robert Chunhua Zhao]]","[[Author/R. C. Zhao]]","[[Author/Robert Chunhua Zhao]]","[[Author/Sasanka Chakrabarti]]","[[Author/S. Chakrabarti]]","[[Author/Sasanka Chakrabarti]]","[[Author/Ilia Stambler]]","[[Author/Ilia Stambler]]","[[Author/Ilia Stambler]]","[[Author/I. Stambler]]","[[Author/Kunlin Jin]]","[[Author/Kunlin Jin]]","[[Author/K. Jin]]","[[Author/Lee Wei Lim]]","[[Author/Lee Wei Lim]]"],"attachment":[],"related":[[]]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},
